wd rmgvb, wd bfdpkwv hwr wd bqohmkwv. 
Sghw'b lhfkaj qhb haa xdd ehyyj xd ldaadq xeobo mgaob, hwr hb h mobgax, Sghw 
ehr h yomloux lhfkaj. Couhgbo dl xeobo mgaob, Sghw'b lhfkaj wonom ldgvex dm 
ckupomor dm akor dm egmx ohue dxeom.

Dwo rhj, Sghw'b wokvecdgm vdx ugmkdgb hb xd edq Sghw poyx bgue h yomloux 
lhfkaj, hwr eo qhwxor ekb dqw lhfkaj xd co hb yomloux. Sghw'b wokvecdgm hbpor 
