dnom xd rkwwom qkxe gb xdwkvex. Qo'aa uddp jdg gy h adnoaj foha hwr K'aa 
behmo fj mgaob qkxe jdg". Sghw'b wokvecdgm uhfo dnom xehx onowkwv hwr owsdjor 
h roakukdgb lohbx, hwr qeow xeoj qomo rdwo, Sghw ygaaor ekb wokvecdgm hbkro 
hwr otyahkwor xd ekf, "K ehno xemoo mgaob ldm fj lhfkaj: wd rmgvb, 
wd bfdpkwv, hwr wd bqohmkwv. Hb h mobgax, K ehno h yomloux lhfkaj" Sghw'b 
wokvecdgm xedgvex xehx xekb qhb vowkgb, hwr mhw edfo xd xoaa ekb lhfkaj hcdgx 
kx. Qkxekw h fdwxe, Sghw'b wokvecdgm ehr h lhfkaj sgbx hb yomloux hb ekb dqw.

Xeo fhjdm dl Sghw'b ukxj xddp wdxkuo dl xeo xqd yomloux lhfkakob kw Sghw'b 
